title: 07/02/21 DPS Hour 2 Channing Frye
itunes:title: 07/02/21 DPS Hour 2 Channing Frye
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, NBA veteran and Turner Sports NBA analyst Channing Frye shares his excitement over the Milwaukee Bucks' supporting cast getting a Game 5 win without Giannis' help. Plus, Dan and company debate the best condiments for a hamburger before a gluttonous 4th of July holiday.
